Accept: application/json

### Product KPI 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analytics/kpis/products?from=2026-05-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-06-01T00:00:00Z&limit=20
Accept: application/json

### Keyword KPI 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analytics/kpis/keywords?from=2026-05-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-06-01T00:00:00Z&limit=20
Accept: application/json

